snippet.textDisplay:
As the coronavirus continues to spread, an increasing number of residential districts in cities and villages have blocked their roads and entrances, including those with no infected residents. Many practitioners say it’s now hard to clarify the truth because the streets are deserted; it's difficult to even visit fellow practitioners’ homes. Some think it's fine to just stay home and study the Fa.

As soon as I heard that one practitioner’s district had started using passes I immediately sent forth righteous thoughts to deny the old forces’ arrangements that are hindering us from offering salvation to people. This is not Master Li's arrangement and we must completely deny it.

When the persecution began in 1999, checkpoints were set up at train stations to keep practitioners from going to Beijing to appeal. However, some practitioners were so determined that they walked all the way to Beijing. Where have our righteous thoughts gone? What can prevent us from offering salvation to sentient beings? A virus? No, it’s our notions. We have accepted this lockdown and allowed it to block us.

If we step forward and try, we’ll find that it’s not difficult.

Master told us:

“When it seems impossible to do, or just hard to do, give it a try and see just what you can do. And when you can really do it, just like that worn and weary traveler, you’ll see, ‘the shade of willows, the blooms of flowers, a place to rest my head’!” (The Ninth Talk, Zhuan Falun)

I recently went out to distribute informational brochures. As I approached the gate to a residential compound, I thought, “What should I say if the security guard questions me?” My second thought was, “No, I shouldn’t think like that. I’m here to offer salvation. He won't challenge me.” Protected by Master, I was able to enter without a problem.

The streets were nearly empty, but I was able to talk to a few people who happened to be out. All of them accepted what I said.

Two of my fellow practitioners went out at night to hang truth-clarification banners and post sticky notes. They said it was easy because no one was outside. They were also able to visit practitioners' homes without any problem.

Fellow practitioners, let’s remember that Master is protecting us. Offering salvation to people is our responsibility. Nothing can stop us. There are many sharing articles and materials available on the Minghui website about how to save people during these special circumstances. Even writing “Falun Dafa is good. Truthfulness-Compassion-Forbearance is good” where it can be easily seen will help.

Ever since the persecution began, the communist regime has been afraid of us going out to clarify the truth. Some practitioners haven’t been able to break through this. More than 20 years have passed. The authorities have exhausted all their tactics. We should see through their tricks and not waiver under any circumstance. Let’s use our wisdom and compassion and offer salvation to more people!
